# RxJS Rules

- Use `switchMap` for request chains; `combineLatest` for parallel calls.
- Cache read-only streams with `shareReplay(1)`.
- Keep manual subscriptions minimal; prefer `async` pipe.
- For manual subscriptions use `takeUntilDestroyed()` from `@angular/core/rxjs-interop`.
